-- Oetker's Bankhaus Lampe, KKR May Purchase BHF-Bank, FT Deutschland Reports
-- B y   J a n n   B e t t i n g a
-- 2010-10-06T20:45:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/bankhaus-lampe-kkr-may-purchase-bhf-bank-ft-deutschland-says.html
Bankhaus Lampe and Kohlberg Kravis
Roberts & Co. may jointly acquire  Deutsche Bank AG ’s BHF-Bank
AG,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported.  Bankhaus Lampe, the German bank controlled by the Oetker
family, is “examining the acquisition of BHF,” the newspaper
said in a preview of an article to be published tomorrow, citing
an unidentified spokeswoman for Bielefeld-based Bankhaus Lampe.  No attribution was given for the newspaper’s report of
KKR’s interest in the deal.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Jann Bettinga  in Frankfurt at 
 jbettinga@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
